title: BEAUTIFUL CONDO IN REACH BCC!!
posting_body: ['Beautiful apartment.', "Live in the best line of BRICKELL CITY CENTRE's REACH CONDO!", 'Stunning city views from this HUGE 3beds/ 3+1/2 baths + dining area + DEN.', 'Top of the line white lacquer cabinetry, Quartz stone counter tops w/ premium Bosch appliances, Marble flooring throughout.', "Reach Condo offers its residents a full-time concierge, gym, Spa, kid's playground, screening room & ultra luxury services.", "Enjoy BCC's high fashion shops, eateries & more!", 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
